  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "In Majesco's Kids Cards, players can choose single-player games or link up with up to three friends in multi-player mode. The fluid interface allows for easy pick-up and play and features unique settings for each of the five card games. The game also features three soundtracks to enhance the overall game play experience. Included games are Go Fish, War, Crazy Eights, Old Maid and Slap Jack.",
